{"tid":1593301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［逆向思維］其實d棄屍浮屍真係班狗搞出來？","createTime":"2019-09-25T04:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T18:16:52.000Z","uid":205394,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4fe62fe9454a530de4634ed25e787e50584dfeb0","tid":1593301,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:13:59.000Z","msg":"答案擺到明就係<br />\n但擺撚到明<br />\n明到一個令人不寒而慄既程度<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n班狗唔係on9，起碼處理屍體咁大件事點會咁草率？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地令人質疑既原因</span></span><br />\n-短期內處理咁多屍體<br />\n-輿論大眾已經開始質疑，甚至有大量文宣，佢地仍然繼續做<br />\n-幾乎無搵過死者家屬澄清<br />\n-對外公布無遺書無可疑<br />\n-光天化日下著住警隊制服去做疑似棄屍行為<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">提問</span></span><br />\n-警署內都有檢屍房等設施可以儲放屍體，點解短期內要棄咁多屍？<br />\n-人都可以暗地裡送返中國，屍體點解唔送返中國再棄？真係想搵都搵唔返<br />\n-對外公布有可疑，查緊，但之後可以唔查架姐，卻偏偏公布無可疑<br />\n-點解唔夜晚搞？成日比人影到佢地用警車著制服去搞棄屍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">結論</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地專登做到出面</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢地擺明話緊比人知<br />\n反抗佢地既下場就係死<br />\n佢地當然唔可以堂堂正正咁講<br />\n但做到咁出面就係想你地知<br />\n所以其實唔洗再懷疑咁多<br />\n<br />\n所以大家唔好再以為搵到佢地棄屍既證據係核彈<br />\n佢地就係想你公諸於眾<br />\n而家我地面對緊既係一個草菅人命既政權<br />\n大家要做好覺悟<br />\n已經唔係一個可以靠輿論同犧牲去制裁既政權<br />\n<br />\n逆向去諗<br />\n既然佢地唔怕我地輿論，只係想我地退縮<br />\n我地唔可以退縮<br />\n我地要比以前更勇武更多人<br />\n等佢地知呢種手段無用<br />\n先有機會制止佢地繼續暗地裡殺我地手足<br />\n<br />\n然後我地要贏，一定要黑警以命賠命<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9303ebd05e6c34d97864d613bd1f0c37d45bfb75","tid":1593301,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"a859dd8d1d69b295d6fccef795a863f206110c73","tid":1593301,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a4e1534399d703e79fc6bc9c1a8bb4af2d0c540b","tid":1593301,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:17:41.000Z","msg":"[國際行動整合]入黎搞清楚攬炒對象同方法，拒做free-rider<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593078</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ac4daea36273545611023635677226e631d6fb7","tid":1593301,"uid":65380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"思路正確"},{"pid":"98960a5a618a0ca52da26a827c821373d45abd40","tid":1593301,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"有道理 推"},{"pid":"c5fc6970da29b20d31cf86bc660843636e55fe45","tid":1593301,"uid":247840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:22:12.000Z","msg":"終於有人講人話"},{"pid":"ee29da9060b6557e404cc9778a9c6d694fdf8d01","tid":1593301,"uid":247840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"同 九品芝麻官 哩個橋段一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5wGNVcflAI8?t=5576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5wGNVcflAI8%3Ft%3D5576&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9F8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=9d298c6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5wGNVcflAI8?t=5576</a>"},{"pid":"1e4e27df747ab35c6ca5832bcf347940b0e6dd68","tid":1593301,"uid":247840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee29da9060b6557e404cc9778a9c6d694fdf8d01","tid":1593301,"uid":247840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25